data.description:
A chance to live in lovely Belle Chasse.  Come see this adorable 3 bedroom 2 bath home recently updated with new flooring, etc.  Spacious den open to the kitchen.  New flooring in the primary bedroom.  Large back yard for entertaining.  Have to see it to appreciate how nice it really is.
It has been shored by Davie Shoring and the lifetime warranty is transferrable to the new owner.  Flood insurance is $633.00 a year and is assumable.  Call now for an appointment.
